Package production

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioPlayer
    The AudioPlayer class is a subclass of the Product class and implements all of the methods contained inside the MultimediaControl interface.
    Controller
    The Controller class implements most of the logic behind the JavaFX application.
    EmployeeLogin
    The EmployeeLogin class is used as the Controller to the employee login screen.
    MoviePlayer
    The MoviePlayer class is a subclass of the Product class and implements all the methods contained inside the MultimediaControl interface.
    Product
    The class Product is used to implement the Item interface.
    ProductionLine
    The ProductionLine class holds the start() method for the JavaFX project.
    Screen
    The Screen class is used to set and get the details of the movie products.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ItemType
    The Enum ItemType is used to hold all of the values for the choice box and their associated "codes".
    MonitorType
    Enum MonitorType is used to hold all the values for the visual products and are LCD or LED.
